name: AVCaptureDevice.SystemPressureState.Level
desc: A structure to represent the system pressure level.

items.name: static let nominal: AVCaptureDevice.SystemPressureState.Level
items.desc: System pressure level is normal (not pressured).

items.name: static let serious: AVCaptureDevice.SystemPressureState.Level
items.desc: System pressure is highly elevated. Capture performance may be impacted. Frame rate throttling is advised.

items.name: static let critical: AVCaptureDevice.SystemPressureState.Level
items.desc: System pressure is critically elevated. Capture quality and performance are significantly impacted. Frame rate throttling is highly advised.

items.name: static let shutdown: AVCaptureDevice.SystemPressureState.Level
items.desc: System pressure is beyond critical, so the capture system has shut down.

items.name: init(rawValue: String)
items.desc: Initializes a system pressure level from its raw string value.
